    public interface ResourceNamesSupplier
extends com.google.common.base.Supplier<com.google.common.collect.SetMultimap<java.lang.Class<? extends Listener>,java.lang.String>>
    A class that can supply a set multimap of Listener classes to Resource names. More formally, instances of this class supply set multimaps with Class<? extends Listener> as keys and String as values.
